comment: Collison (SAC) commits a take foul on Jordan (LAC).
Collison (SAC) commits an away from the play foul on Jordan (LAC).
Collison (SAC) does not beat Paul (LAC) to the spot (point of contact).
Belinelli (SAC) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes into the backcourt.
[Observable in enhanced video] Paul (LAC) makes incidental contact with Collison (SAC).
Griffin (LAC) makes a legitimate basketball move to start his dribble, and Rondo (SAC), who is defending Griffin closely, absorbs contact as Griffin steps forward.
Koufos (SAC) bumps Griffin (LAC) and the contact affects his shooting movement.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Belinelli's (SAC) made field goal was taken in the three-point arc was upheld.
Casspi (SAC) commits a take foul on Redick (LAC).
